# =============================================================================
# DECISIONING + BENCHMARK EXTENSIONS
# These are intentionally post-estimation helpers. They keep the Stan model
# focused on estimation while adding Meridian/Robyn-style decision outputs:
# calibration checks, ROI/mROI, budget optimization, reach/frequency prep,
# and sensitivity runs.
# =============================================================================

